        "timestamp": "2018-05-15 20:18:57.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nIt was suggested to use 10003 repo instead of 10004 since ONAP does not use the later. Related to help desk item 55557. This build failed because not authorised to push to https://jenkins.onap.org/view/vfc/job/vfc-nfvo-driver-svnfm-nokiav2-docker-vnfm-nokiav2-master-release-version-docker-daily-no-sonar/17/console\n10004. I am not completely sure if this is the right solution.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "68034e59d0bd43c869da03fd2846ab0950093ca8",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2255,
          "name": "Dénes Németh",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "denes.nemeth@nokia.com",
          "username": "thelittlemouse"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-05-15 20:21:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> (1 comment)\n\n\"Denes,\n\nCan you please try pushing this into 10003 rather than 10004?\n\nI know this is confusing, but chatting with Andy I believe there are old\nreasons why 10004 is not being used as a staging repository at all.\nSeems like ONAP decided to continue using 10003 for both staging and snapshots in\nNexus3.\n\nPlease try that and let's see if that allows you to push.\n\nthanks!\"\n\nI tried to add in an other parameter that switches between the build mode and is independent from the docker registry.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
