        "timestamp": "2018-05-15 20:25:48.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nYea,, that suggestion was made by me. \nWe should pass this variable in your project's YAML not on the job \ntemplate. \n\nIn your project's yaml, you will need to set the varaible \nDOCKERREGISTRY to 10003\n\nI asked Jeremy to give us a hand too since we are little bit overloaded.",
